    "components": [
      {
        "name": "Floating Pill Navigation",
        "role": "Primary site navigation",
        "description": "Dark Carbon Black (#18181b) pill-shaped bar, ~15px radius, floats over hero imagery with generous internal padding (~12px vertical, ~19px horizontal). Logo wordmark left in white, center nav links in white/60 opacity, orange Sunrise Coral CTA button right. The floating pill is a signature element — it never sticks to viewport edges but always appears as a contained capsule."
      },
      {
        "name": "Primary Pill CTA",
        "role": "Primary conversion button",
        "description": "Sunrise Coral (#fc5f2b) fill, white text at 15-17px weight 700, 9999px border-radius, ~15px vertical × ~24-32px horizontal padding. Tight letter-spacing (-0.009em). Right-arrow chevron after label. No drop shadow — relies on color contrast alone."
      },
      {
        "name": "Ghost Text Link",
        "role": "Secondary navigation and inline links",
        "description": "No background, no border. White or Carbon Black text at 13-15px weight 400 with tight tracking. Underline appears on hover only. Used for nav items and inline content links."
      },
      {
        "name": "Hero Overlay Headline",
        "role": "Hero section primary heading",
        "description": "66px display size, weight 400 (NOT 700 — the whisper-weight is deliberate), line-height 1.0, letter-spacing -0.025em, white (#ffffff) text, centered over full-bleed dark photography. This weight-400-at-display-size choice is the system's most distinctive typographic decision."
      },
      {
        "name": "Hero Subhead",
        "role": "Hero supporting copy",
        "description": "17px body-lg, weight 400, Zinc Gray (#71717a) on white sections, white at reduced opacity on dark hero. Centered, max-width ~480px."
      },
      {
        "name": "Membership Visual Card",
        "role": "Hero/pricing card artwork",
        "description": "Organic marbled pattern in Sunrise Coral gradient (linear 88deg from #fc5f2b to #ff8b64 fading to white), 15px radius, ~320px wide. Contains 'superpower membership' wordmark top-left and '$17/month' price block bottom-left in white. The only decorative visual on the site."
      },
      {
        "name": "Membership Feature List",
        "role": "Bullet list of membership benefits",
        "description": "Vertical list with Sunrise Coral checkmark icons (7.5px radius squircle), 19px body text in Carbon Black, 11px row gap. Checks are filled solid coral, not outlined."
      },
      {
        "name": "Section Heading",
        "role": "Major section titles",
        "description": "45-56px heading-lg/display, weight 400, letter-spacing -0.015 to -0.022em, Carbon Black. Generous bottom margin (~30-40px). Left-aligned in content sections, centered over imagery."
      },
      {
        "name": "FAQ Item / Read More",
        "role": "Expandable content blocks",
        "description": "Large heading at 30-37px paired with a small ghost-style 'Read more' text link right-aligned. No box, no border — relies on whitespace and type size for separation."
      },
      {
        "name": "Trust Badge Row",
        "role": "Credibility indicators (HSA/FSA, payment methods)",
        "description": "Horizontal row of small icons and labels at 11-13px, Zinc Gray text, with tiny check or icon glyphs in Carbon Black. Sits directly below primary CTA as a conversion reassurance pattern."
      },
      {
        "name": "Photo Thumbnail Strip",
        "role": "Image carousel/dashboard previews",
        "description": "Horizontal row of 5-6 small rectangular thumbnails (~80-100px wide), 5px radius, showing app/dashboard screenshots. One thumbnail is active with a Sunrise Coral border."
      }
    ],
    "typography": [
      {
        "role": "Everything — display, headings, body, UI, nav. The signature choice is the aggressively tight negative tracking that scales with size (-0.025em at 66px down to -0.005em at small body) combined with line-heights that compress as sizes grow, giving headlines a monolithic, poster-like density that distinguishes Superpower from airy health-tech competitors",
        "sizes": "11, 13, 15, 17, 19, 22, 26, 30, 37, 45, 56, 60, 66",
        "family": "NB International Pro",
        "weight": "400, 700",
        "lineHeight": "1.00, 1.06, 1.10, 1.13, 1.20, 1.25, 1.40, 1.50",
        "substitute": "Inter Tight, General Sans, Switzer",
        "letterSpacing": "-0.0250em, -0.0220em, -0.0200em, -0.0150em, -0.0130em, -0.0120em, -0.0090em, -0.0050em"
      },
      {
        "role": "Tabular metadata, micro-copy annotations, technical labels — used sparingly for moments requiring a clinical/instrumented feel",
        "sizes": "11, 13",
        "family": "NB International Mono Pro",
        "weight": "400",
        "lineHeight": "1.40, 1.50",
        "substitute": "JetBrains Mono, IBM Plex Mono",
        "letterSpacing": "-0.0060em"
      }
    ],
    "description": "Superpower wraps a serious clinical promise in cinematic, atmospheric UI: full-bleed dark photography heroes transition into crisp white content surfaces, with one vivid sunrise-orange accent pulsing through the system. Typography carries the brand — a proprietary geometric sans at whisper-tight negative tracking, scaling from 11px metadata to 66px display with line-heights that compress as sizes grow (1.00 at display, 1.40–1.50 at body). A floating dark pill navigation bar hovers over imagery, and pill-shaped CTAs create a tension between clinical precision and warm vitality. Surfaces are mostly flat — the system relies on generous white space, hairline zinc dividers, and a single faint shadow pattern rather than heavy elevation. Color is rationed: nearly everything is black, white, or zinc-gray, and the orange appears only as functional punctuation on actions and brand marks.",
    "customSections": [
      {
        "title": "Agent Prompt Guide",
        "content": "**Quick Color Reference**\n- text: #18181b (Carbon Black)\n- background: #ffffff (Paper White)\n- border: #e4e4e7 (Mist Gray)\n- muted text: #71717a (Zinc Gray)\n- accent: #fc5f2b (Sunrise Coral)\n- primary action: no distinct CTA color\n\n**3 Example Component Prompts**\n\nNo distinct primary action color was observed; use the extracted neutral button treatments instead of inventing a filled CTA color.\n\n\n3. **FAQ Section**: White background, max-width 1200px centered. 'Frequently Asked Questions' heading at 45px weight 400 #18181b, left-aligned, 75px top margin. FAQ items: 30px question text in #18181b weight 400, 'Read more' ghost text link right-aligned at 13px #71717a. 11px row gap between items, no dividers or borders."
      }
    ],
    "elevationPhilosophy": "Elevation is deliberately restrained — a single 2px/2px hairline shadow on cards. The system prefers flat surfaces with hairline borders to communicate layering rather than casting shadows, letting the full-bleed photography do the heavy visual lifting."
  },
